sections.text: Effective date1-103.Effective dateEach and all of the laws and statutes as herein contained and hereby enacted shall take effect and be in force on and after twelve o'clock noon on January 9, 1956, except where a later effective date is expressly provided in any section of these Revised Statutes, the later effective date shall prevail.
